: : Rodimus Prime : :

Rodimus' somber mood lightened up with Windlord's message. He opened a return channel.

Rodimus: Thank you, Windlord. Thank you for bringing my wife back to me. Contact Rhinox about getting that thing off her. Kup is dealing with a... delicate matter as we speak. I'll be down when I have a chance. Rodimus out.

He closes the link.
